title: Lenmar Replacement Rechargeable battery for Canon NB-4L; compatible with Canon Digital IXUS 30, 40, 50, 55, 60, 65, 70, 75, 80 IS, i7, PowerShot ELPH 100 HS, ELPH 300 HS,ELPH 310 HS, SD1000, SD1100 IS, SD1400 IS, SD200, SD30, SD300, SD40, SD400, SD430, SD450, SD600, SD630, SD750, SD780 IS, SD940 IS, SD960 IS, SD970 IS, TX1.
description: Keep a spare battery on hand for your Canon SD300 or SD200 digital camera with this NB-4L equivalent Lithium-ion battery from Lenmar. It features 3.7 volts and 760 mAh of power and includes a 3-year warranty.
